{"prompt": "Generate a website for a smart home technology. The website should be playful and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SmartHome Fun!</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f0f0f0;\n            color: #333;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b, #e74c3c);\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1000px;\n            margin: 40px auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n        .section {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .section h2 {\n            color: #e74c3c;\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: #ffebee;\n            padding: 25px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            border: 2px solid #ff6b6b;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.3);\n        }\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: #e74c3c;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #c0392b;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #e74c3c;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #ff6b6b;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        /* Simple icons - using emojis for simplicity as actual icon fonts might be too complex for a single HTML file */\n        .icon-bulb::before { content: \"\ud83d\udca1\"; }\n        .icon-lock::before { content: \"\ud83d\udd12\"; }\n        .icon-speaker::before { content: \"\ud83d\udd0a\"; }\n        .icon-thermometer::before { content: \"\ud83c\udf21\ufe0f\"; }\n        .icon-plug::before { content: \"\ud83d\udd0c\"; }\n        .icon-controller::before { content: \"\ud83c\udfae\"; }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>SmartHome Fun!</h1>\n        <p>Your home, smarter and more playful!</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Bring Your Home to Life!</h2>\n            <p>Imagine a home that anticipates your needs, plays your favorite tunes, and keeps you safe \u2013 all with a tap or a voice command. SmartHome Fun! makes it a reality with easy-to-use, delightful technology.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"section\">\n            <h2>What Can You Do?</h2>\n            <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <span class=\"icon-bulb\"></span>\n                    <h3>Lighting Magic</h3>\n                    <p>Set the mood with colorful, smart lighting. Dim, brighten, or change colors to match your vibe.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <span class=\"icon-lock\"></span>\n                    <h3>Secure & Sound</h3>\n                    <p>Keep your home safe with smart locks and security cameras, all controllable from your phone.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <span class=\"icon-speaker\"></span>\n                    <h3>Music Everywhere</h3>\n                    <p>Fill your home with music. Play different songs in different rooms or sync them up for parties.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <span class=\"icon-thermometer\"></span>\n                    <h3>Perfect Climate</h3>\n                    <p>Control your heating and cooling remotely. Save energy and always come home to comfort.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <span class=\"icon-plug\"></span>\n                    <h3>Smart Plugs</h3>\n                    <p>Make any appliance smart! Turn coffee makers, fans, or lamps on/off with your app.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <span class=\"icon-controller\"></span>\n                    <h3>Automate Your Day</h3>\n                    <p>Create fun routines! \"Good Morning\" can turn on lights, start the coffee, and play the news.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Ready to Play?</h2>\n            <p>Discover how easy and fun smart home technology can be. Get started today and transform your living space!</p>\n            <button class=\"cta-button\" onclick=\"alert('Thanks for your interest! \\nExplore our playful products at smartomefun.example.com')\">Get Started Now!</button>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 SmartHome Fun! All rights reserved. Let's make home awesome!</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}